version_description: With this update, we're introducing a year calendar view! Now you can see your cycle data not only by month but also a trend of your cycle throughout a year. We've also made bug fixes and performance updates so you could focus on tracking your cycle witho

With this update, we're introducing a year calendar view! Now you can see your cycle data not only by month but also a trend of your cycle throughout a year. We've also made bug fixes and performance updates so you could focus on tracking your cycle witho
